<h3 id="6-ftp-Л└°К╧└Л┼╓-К║°Й╥╦-Й╦╟К║²">6. FTP Л└°К╧└Л┼╓ К║°Й╥╦ Й╦╟К║²</h3>
<ul>
  <li>FTP Л└°К╧└Л┼╓ Й╦╟К▐≥ Л▀°Л≈░ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-l</code> Л≤╣Л┘≤Л²└ К╤─Л≈╛М∙╢Л└° Л▀╓М√┴М∙≤К╘╢ xferlog М▄▄Л²╪Л²└ Й╦╟К║²</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Sat Oct 29 21:35:39 2016 1 1.226.137.47 70 /home/devtest/aa.html a _ i r devtest ftp 0 * c</code>
    <ul>
      <li>70 : М▄▄Л²╪Л═└Л├║ М│╛Й╦╟</li>
      <li>i : М▄▄Л²╪ Л≈┘К║°К⌠°</li>
      <li>c : Л└╠ЙЁ╣ (i=Л▀╓М▄╗)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Sat Oct 29 22:58:38 2016 1 110.15.241.24 70 /home/devtest/aa.html b _ o r devtest ftp 0 * c</code>
    <ul>
      <li>o : М▄▄Л²╪ К▀╓Л ╢К║°К⌠°</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

