<h3 id="2-pemprivacy-enhanced-mail">2. PEM(Privacy Enhanced Mail)</h3>
<ul>
  <li>М■└К²╪Л²╢К╡└Л▀° М√╔Л┐│ Л²╢К╘■Л²╪</li>
  <li>Л╓▒Л∙≥Л╖▒Л╓▒М≥■К░° М┌╓ Л²╦Л╕² К╟╘Л▀²</li>
  <li>Й╣╛М≤└Л²╢ Л√╢К═╣ЙЁ═ К├▓Л²─ КЁ╢Л∙┬Л└╠ Л═°ЙЁ╣ (Й╣╟Л┌╛, Л²─М√┴)</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="3-smimesecure-multi-purpose-internet-mail-extensions">3. S/MIME(Secure Multi-Purpose Internet Mail Extensions)</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Й╟°Л ■
    <ul>
      <li>М▒°Л╓─ КЁ╢Л∙┬ К╘■Л²╪ Й╥°Л∙╫, Л├║Л▀═Л·░Л≥─ Л┬≤Л▀═Л·░К╔╪ Л²╦Л╕², К╘■Л▀°Л╖─ К╛╢Й╡╟Л└╠ Л╕²К╙┘, Л╡╗К╤─М▄▄Л²╪</li>
      <li>К╘■Л▀°Л╖─ К┌╢Л ╘Л²≤ PrivacyК╔╪ КЁ╢Л╕²М∙≤К┼■ М▒°Л╓─ КЁ╢Л∙┬ К╘■Л²╪ М■└К║°М├═Л╫°, К╘■Л²╪ Л═└Л╡╢К╔╪ Л∙■М≤╦М≥■</li>
      <li>Л²╦М└╟К└╥ MIME К╘■Л▀°Л╖─Л≈░ Л═└Л·░ Л└°К╙┘ЙЁ╪ М∙╗Й╩≤ Л∙■М≤╦М≥■К╔╪ К█■М∙° М■└К║°М├═Л╫°К║°Л└° RSA Л∙■М≤╦ Л┌╛Л ╘</li>
      <li>CA(Л²╦Л╕²Й╦╟Й╢─)К║°К╤─М└╟ Л·░Л▀═Л²≤ ЙЁ╣Й╟°М┌╓К╔╪ КЁ╢Л╕²М∙≤К┼■ Л²╦Л╕²Л└°К╔╪ К╟⌡Л∙└Л∙╪ М∙╗</li>
      <li>Л╡╗К╤─ М▄▄Л²╪Л²└ КЁ╢Л∙┬</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>S/MIMEЛ≈░ Л┌╛Л ╘К░≤К┼■ Л∙■М≤╦М≥■ М┌╓
    <ul>
      <li>DSS : К■■Л╖─М└╦ Л└°К╙┘ Л∙▄ЙЁ═К╕╛Л╕≤</li>
      <li>3Л╓▒ DES : К╘■Л▀°Л╖─Л²≤ Л∙■М≤╦</li>
      <li>SHA-1 : К■■Л╖─М└╦ Л└°К╙┘Л²└ Л╖─Л⌡░М∙≤Й╦╟ Л°└М∙° М∙╢Л▀°М∙╗Л┬≤
        <h1 id="sendmail-КЁ╢Л∙┬">Sendmail КЁ╢Л∙┬</h1>
        <h2 id="1-sendmail">1. Sendmail</h2>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>К▄─М▒°Л═│Л²╦ Mail Transport Agent(MTA)</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="2-sendmail-Л ╢Л≤│-К╙╗К⌠°">2. Sendmail Л ╢Л≤│ К╙╗К⌠°</h2>
<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/usr/sbin/sendmail -&lt;Option&gt;</code>
    <ul>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-bd</code> : К█╟К╙╛ К╙╗К⌠°К║° Л▀╓М√┴</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-bi</code> : Л∙╗К╕╛Л√╢Л┼╓ К█╟Л²╢М└╟К╡═Л²╢Л┼╓ М▄▄Л²╪Л²└ Л╢┬Й╦╟М≥■</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-bm</code> : Be a mail sender(MDAК╖▄Л²≤ Й╦╟К┼╔Л°╪К║° Л·▒К▐≥)</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-bp</code> : М│░Л≈░ Л·┬К┼■ К┌╢Л ╘Л²└ М■└К╕╟М└╟</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-bs</code> : М▒°Л╓─ Л·┘К═╔Л°╪К║° SMTPК╔╪ Л▀╓М√┴</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-bt</code> : М┘▄Л┼╓М┼╦ К╙╗К⌠°, rewriteК╔╪ М┘▄Л┼╓М┼╦М∙≤Й╦╟ Л°└М∙╢ Л²╢Л ╘</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-bv</code> : М≥∙Л²╦ К╙╗К⌠°</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Л⌡° К╟▐ К╟■Л²╢К÷╛Л┼╓ М≈╓К█■К╔╪ Л·┘К═╔М∙° М⌡└ Й╡╟ЙЁ╪К║° М∙└М└╟К╖│ К▐≥Л·▒ Л≈╛К╤─К╔╪ М≥∙Л²╦
    <ul>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/etc/mail/sendmail.cf</code> : Кё╟Л┘▀</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"># /usr/lib/sendmail -bt</code> : М┘▄Л┼╓М┼╦ К╙╗К⌠° Л▀╓М√┴</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&gt; check_nv boundary="====_ABC1234567890DEF_====</code> : NIMDA worm test</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h2 id="3-sendmail-Л═▒Й╥╪-М▄▄Л²╪spam-mail-Л╟╗К▀╗">3. Sendmail Л═▒Й╥╪ М▄▄Л²╪(SPAM Mail Л╟╗К▀╗)</h2>
<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/etc/mail/access</code> Л·▒Л└╠ Й╥°Л╧≥
    <ul>
      <li>OK : К▀╓К╔╦ ruleЛ²╢ Й╠╟К╤─М∙≤Л≈╛К▐└ К⌠╓Л√╢Л≤╓К┼■ К╘■Л²╪Л²└ К╟⌡Л∙└К⌠╓Л·└</li>
      <li>RELAY : relayК╔╪ М≈┬Л ╘, К▀╓К╔╦ ruleЛ²╢ Й╠╟К╤─М∙≤К┼■ Й╡╫Л ╟К▐└ Л╖─Л═∙К░° М┼╧Л═∙ К▐└К╘■Л²╦Л²╢ Л·┬К┼■ Л┌╛Л ╘Л·░Л≈░Й╡▄ Л≤╓К┼■ К╘■Л²╪Л²└ К╟⌡Л²▄</li>
      <li>REJECT : Л┬≤Л▀═ К╟▐ К╟°Л▀═Л²└ Л≥└Л═└М·┬ Й╠╟К╤─</li>
      <li>DISCARD : К╘■Л²╪Л²└ К╟⌡Й╦╟К╖▄ М∙≤ЙЁ═ К╘■Л▀°Л╖─К╔╪ Л≥└Л═└М·┬ М▐░Й╦╟</li>
      <li>501 : Л╖─Л═∙К░° e-mail К≤░К┼■ К▐└К╘■Л²╦Л≈░ К▄─М∙╢ КЁ╢К┌╢К┼■ Л┌╛К·▄Л²≤ Лё╪Л├▄Й╟─ Л═└Л╡╢ К≤░К┼■ К╤─К╤└Л═│Л°╪К║° Л²╪Л╧≤М∙═ Й╡╫Л ╟ К╘■Л²╪ Й╠╟К╤─</li>
      <li>550 : М┼╧Л═∙ К▐└К╘■Л²╦Л≈░ Й╢─К═╗К░° К╘■Л²╪Л²└ Й╠╟К╤─</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/etc/mail/access</code> Л└╓Л═∙
    <ul>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">spam@abc.com    REJECT</code> : К╟°Л├║К░≤К┼■ К╘■Л²╪Л²≤ Л┬≤Л▀═ К╟▐ К╟°Л▀═Л²└ К╙╗К▒░ Й╠╟К╤─</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">spammail.com    REJECT</code> : К╟°Л├║К░≤К┼■ К╘■Л²╪Л²≤ Л┬≤Л▀═ К╟▐ К╟°Л▀═Л²└ К╙╗К▒░ Й╠╟К╤─</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">attacker.com    DISCARD</code> : Л┬≤Л▀═ К╟▐ К╟°Л▀═ К╙╗К▒░К╔╪ М▐░Й╦╟ (К╟°Л▀═Л·░Л≈░Й╡▄ М▐░Й╦╟М├╣КЁ╢ X)</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">useful.org      OK</code> : К╘■Л²╪Л²└ Л┬≤Л▀═</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">201.1.1         RELAY</code> : 201.1.1.0/24Л≈░Л└° К╟°Л├║К░≤К┼■ К╙╗К⌠═ К╘■Л²╪Л²≤ Л┬≤Л▀═ К╟▐ К╟°Л▀═Л²└ М≈┬Л ╘ (Л╓▒ЙЁ└Л≈╜М∙═)</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">211.1.1         RELAY</code> : 2101.1.1.0/24Л≈░Л└° К╟°Л├║К░≤К┼■ К╙╗К⌠═ К╘■Л²╪Л²≤ Л┬≤Л▀═ К╟▐ К╟°Л▀═Л²└ М≈┬Л ╘ (Л╓▒ЙЁ└Л≈╜М∙═)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h1 id="Л┼╓М▄╦К╘■Л²╪spam-mail-Л╟╗К▀╗-К╟╘К╡∙">Л┼╓М▄╦К╘■Л²╪(Spam Mail) Л╟╗К▀╗ К╟╘К╡∙</h1>
<h2 id="1-spam-mail-Л╟╗К▀╗-К╟╘К╡∙">1. Spam Mail Л╟╗К▀╗ К╟╘К╡∙</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Spam Mail Л╟╗К▀╗ Й╦╟К╡∙Л²≤ Л╒┘К╔≤</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/images/posts/RBL.gif" alt="RBL" /></p>

<p><a href="https://spam.kisa.or.kr/rbl/sub2_R.do?idx=10&amp;currentPage=1">Л²╢К╞╦Л╖─ Л╤°Л╡≤_RBL</a></p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/posts/spf.png" alt="SPF" /></p>

<p><a href="https://www.cyber.gov.au/acsc/view-all-content/publications/how-combat-fake-emails">Л²╢К╞╦Л╖─ Л╤°Л╡≤_SPF</a></p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: left">RBL(Real Time Blocking)</th>
      <th style="text-align: left">SPF(Sender Policy Framework)</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left"><ul><li>Л┼╓М▄╦К╘■Л²╪Л≈░ Л┌╛Л ╘К░≤К┼■ IP К╕╛Л┼╓М┼╦К╔╪ К⌠╠К║²М∙≤ЙЁ═ Л╟╗К▀╗</li><li>Й╣╜К┌╢ : KISAЛ²≤ RBL Л└°К╡└Л≈░ М┼╧Л═∙ IPК╔╪ К⌠╠К║²М∙≤ЙЁ═ Л╟╗К▀╗М∙╗</li></ul></td>
      <td style="text-align: left"><ul><li>К╟°Л▀═Л·░ : Л·░Л▀═Л²≤ К╘■Л²╪ Л└°К╡└ Л═∙КЁ╢Л≥─ Л═∙Л╠┘Л²└ К┌≤М┐─К┌╢К┼■ SPF К═┬Л╫■К⌠°К╔╪ М∙╢К▀╧ DNSЛ≈░ К⌠╠К║²М∙╗</li><li>Л┬≤Л▀═Л·░ : К╘■Л²╪ Л┬≤Л▀═ Л▀° К╟°Л├║Л·░Л²≤ DNSЛ≈░ К⌠╠К║²К░° SPF К═┬Л╫■К⌠°К╔╪ М≥∙Л²╦М∙≤Л≈╛ М∙╢К▀╧ К╘■Л²╪Л≈░ М▒°Л▀°К░° К╟°Л├║ IPЛ≥─ К╧└Й╣░М∙≤ЙЁ═ Й╥╦ Й╡╟ЙЁ╪Л≈░ К■╟К²╪ Л┬≤Л▀═ Л≈╛К╤─К╔╪ Й╡╟Л═∙М∙╗</li></ul></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2 id="2-spamassassin">2. SpamAssassin</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Л═∙Л²≤ : Л═░Л┬≤К╔╪ Л²╢Л ╘М∙≤Л≈╛ Л┼╓М▄╦ Л≈╛К╤─К╔╪ М▄░К▀╗, PerlК║° Й╟°К╟°К░╗</li>
  <li>М┼╧Л╖∙ : Rule Й╦╟К╟≤ М∙≤Л≈░ HeaderЛ≥─ BodyК╔╪ К╤└Л└²М∙≤Л≈╛ Л▀╓Л▀°Й╟└ Л╟╗К▀╗ К╕╛Л┼╓М┼╦ (Internet-based real time blacklist(RBL)) К╔╪ Л╟╦ЙЁ═М∙≤Л≈╛ Й╟│Й╟│Л²≤ Кё╟Л≈░ К╖╓Л╧╜К░═ Й╡╫Л ╟ Л═░Л┬≤К╔╪ К╖╓Й╡╗Л└° Л╢² Л═░Л┬≤Й╟─ Й╦╟Л╓─Л═░Л²└ Л╢┬ЙЁ╪М∙≤К┼■Л╖─ Л≈╛К╤─Л≈░ К■╟К²╪ Л┼╓М▄╦ Л≈╛К╤─К╔╪ Й╡╟Л═∙</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="Л⌡╧-Л└°К╡└-КЁ╢Л∙┬web-server-security"><strong>Л⌡╧ Л└°К╡└ КЁ╢Л∙┬(Web Server Security)</strong></h1>
<h2 id="1-Л⌡╧world-wide-web-Й╟°Л ■">1. Л⌡╧(World Wide Web) Й╟°Л ■</h2>
<h3 id="1-wwwworld-wide-web">1. WWW(World Wide Web)</h3>
<ul>
  <li>К╘■К┴╢ К╟╘Л▀²Л°╪К║° Л└°К╧└Л┼╓М∙≤К█≤ Й╦╟Л║╢Л²≤ Л²╦М└╟К└╥ Л└°К╧└Л┼╓К╔╪ Tim Berners-Lee Л²≤ Л═°Л∙┬Л°╪К║° М∙≤Л²╢М█╪М┘█Л┼╓М┼╦К╔╪ Й╦╟К╟≤Л°╪К║° Л⌡╧К╛╦Л└°К╔╪ М≥°Л ╘М∙≤Л≈╛ М▌╦Л²≤Л└╠Л²└ М√╔Л┐│Л▀°М┌╗ Л└°К╧└Л┼╓</li>
</ul>

