<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: left">КЁ╢Л∙┬ Л└╓Л═∙</th>
      <th style="text-align: left">К┌╢Л ╘</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Лё╪Л ■ К■■К═┴М└╟К╕╛ К╟▐ М▄▄Л²╪ Л═▒Й╥╪ Й╤▄М∙°</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">RootЛ≈░ Л²≤М∙╢ Л▀╓М√┴ Й╟─К┼╔М∙° К╙╗К⌠═ К╙┘К═╧Л√╢К┼■ К▀╓К╔╦ Л┌╛Л ╘Л·░Й╟─ Л┬≤Л═∙М∙≤Л╖─ К╙╩М∙≤К▐└К║² Л└╓Л═∙<br />&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"># chown 0. bin conf logs</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"># chgrp 0. bin conf logs</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#chmod 755 . bin conf logs</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#chmod 511 /user/loca/httpd/bin/httpd</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;{:/}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">К╤┬М∙└Л ■М∙° М▄▄Л²╪ Л┌╜Л═°</td>
      <td style="text-align: left"><ul><li>Л∙└М▄▄Л╧≤ Л└╓Л╧≤ Л▀° Й╦╟КЁ╦Л═│Л°╪К║° Л└╓Л╧≤К░≤К┼■ cgi-binЛ²─ ЙЁ╣Й╡╘Л≈░ Л²╢Л ╘К░═ Л┬≤ Л·┬Л°╪К╞─К║° Л┌╜Л═°</li><li>К╖╓К┴╢Л√╪ М▄▄Л²╪Л²─ Л▀°Л┼╓М┘°Л≈░ К▄─М∙° Л═∙КЁ╢К╔╪ Л═°ЙЁ╣М∙═ Л┬≤ Л·┬Л√╢Л└° ЙЁ╣Й╡╘Л≈░ К▐└Л⌡─Л²╢ К░═ Л┬≤ Л·┬Л°╪К╞─К║° Л┌╜Л═°</li><li>/var/www/manual К╟▐ /var/www/cgi_bin Л┌╜Л═°</li></ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Directory Listing</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">index.htmlЛ²╢ Л≈├Й╠╟К┌≤ ListingЛ²└ КЁ╢Л≈╛Лё╪К┼■ Л≤╣Л┘≤Л²╢ indexesЛ≈░ Л└╓Л═∙К░≤Л√╢ Л·┬К┼■ Й╡╫Л ╟ Л⌡╧ М▌≤Л²╢Л╖─Л²≤ К■■К═┴М└╟К╕╛Й╟─ КЁ╢Л·└</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">FollowSynLinks</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Л▀╛КЁ╪К╕╜ К╖│М│╛К╔╪ Л²╢Л ╘М∙╢Л└° М▄▄Л²╪ Л▀°Л┼╓М┘°Л≈░ Л═▒Й╥╪М∙≤Л≈╛ Root Й╤▄М∙°Л²└ М █К⌠²М∙═ Л┬≤ Л·┬Л°╪К╞─К║° FollowSymLinkК╔╪ Л═°Й╠╟</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Directory indexes</td>
      <td style="text-align: left"><ul><li>Л ╟Л└═Л┬°Л°└К╔╪ Й╡╟Л═∙М∙╗</li><li>index.cgi>index.html>index.htmЛ²≤ Л┬°Л└°</li><li>`# DirectoryIndex: sets the file that Apache will serve iof a directory is requested.`</li><li>`<IfModule dir-module>DirectoryIndex index.html</IfModule>`</li></ul></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Server Tokens</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Л⌡╧ Л└°К╡└Л≈░ Л═▒Л├█М∙═ Й╡╫Л ╟ Л╣°Л├▄М∙°Л²≤ Л═∙КЁ╢К╖▄ КЁ╢Л²╢К▐└К║² Л└╓Л═∙</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">ServerSignature</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">ServerSignature on:on Л°╪К║° Л└╓Л═∙К░° Й╡╫Л ╟ Л∙└М▄▄Л╧≤ К╡└Л═└ К╟▐ Л└°К╡└ Л²╢К╕└Л²╢ К┘╦Л╤°К░╗</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Л═▒Й╥╪ Л═°Л√╢</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">М│╢К²╪Л²╢Л√╦М┼╦Л²≤ Л²╢К╕└ К╟▐ IP Лё╪Л├▄ К⌠╠Л²└ Л┌╛Л ╘М∙╢ Л═▒Й╥╪ Л═°Л√╢ Л┬≤М√┴&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;Directory /&gt;</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">    Options FollowSynLinks</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">    AllowOverride None</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">    Order deny,allow</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">    Deny from all</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;/Directory&gt;</code>&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;{:/}</td>
    </tr>
