<h3 id="3-apache-Л⌡╧-Л└°К╡└-httpdconf-М▄▄Л²╪-Л└╓Л═∙">3. Apache Л⌡╧ Л└°К╡└ httpd.conf М▄▄Л²╪ Л└╓Л═∙</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Л≤┬Л▀°
    <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  &lt;Directory "D:/document"&gt;
      Options Indexes FollowSynLinks
      AllowOverride All
      Order Deny, Allow
      Deny from all
      Allow from 127.0.0.1
  &lt;/Directory&gt;
</code></pre></div>    </div>

    <ul>
      <li>Order Deny, Allow
        <ul>
          <li>К╗╪Л═─ Deny, К┌≤Л╓▒Л≈░ Allow</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Deny from all
        <ul>
          <li>Л°└Л²≤ Л└╓Л═∙Л²─ К╙╗К⌠═ М┼╦К·≤М■╫Л²└ К╖┴К┼■К▀╓.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Allow from 127.0.0.1
        <ul>
          <li>1К╡┬Л²≤ order deny, allow К╟▐ 2К╡┬Л²≤ Deny from all Л║╟Й╠╢Л≈░ К■╟К²╪ 127.0.0.1 К╖▄ Л═▒Л├█Л²└ М≈┬Л ╘М∙°К▀╓.</li>
          <li>127.0.0.1 Л²─ localhost Л²╢Й╦╟ К∙▄К╛╦Л≈░ Л·░Л▀═Л²≤ Л╩╢М⌠╗М└╟К╔╪ Л═°Л≥╦М∙° К▀╓К╔╦ ЙЁЁЛ≈░Л└°К┼■ Л═▒Л├█Л²╢ К╤┬Й╟─К┼╔М∙° Л┐│М┐°К║° Л└╓Л═∙М∙°К▀╓.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>httpd.conf М┼╧Л═∙ IP Лё╪Л├▄К╖▄ Л╟╗К▀╗
    <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  &lt;Directory "D:/document"&gt;
      Options Indexes FollowSynLinks
      AllowOverride All
      Order Allow, Deny
      Deny from all
      Allow from 210.1.1.1
  &lt;/Directory&gt;
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ServerTokens [OS|Prod]</code>
    <ul>
      <li>OS : HTTP Response Л²▒К▀╣ Л▀° HeaderЛ²≤ Server М∙└К⌠°Л≈░ Л⌡╧ Л└°К╡└ К╡└Л═└ЙЁ╪ Л ╢Л≤│Л╡╢Л═° Л═∙КЁ╢К╔╪ Л═°ЙЁ╣</li>
      <li>Prod : HTTP Response Л²▒К▀╣ Л▀° HeaderЛ²≤ Server М∙└К⌠°Л≈░ Л⌡╧ Л└°К╡└ Л╒┘К╔≤К╖▄ Л═°ЙЁ╣</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

