<h3 id="5-Л⌡▄М└╟К╖│-М≥─watering-hole-ЙЁ╣Й╡╘">5. Л⌡▄М└╟К╖│ М≥─(Watering Hole) ЙЁ╣Й╡╘</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Л⌡▄М└╟К╖│ М≥─ ЙЁ╣Й╡╘(М┼╧Л═∙ М┐─Й╡÷)Л²─ М≥┬М▌≤Л²╢Л╖─Л≈░ Л═▒Л├█М∙≤К┼■ М┼╧Л═∙ Л┌╛М ▄Л═│ Й╥╦Кё╧Л²└ К▄─Л┐│Л°╪К║° Л∙┘Л└╠Л╫■К⌠°К╔╪ Л°═М▐╛М∙≤Л≈╛ М┼╧Л═∙ Л┌╛М ▄Л═│ Й╥╦Кё╧Л≈░ Л╤■Й╟─Л═│Л²╦ APT ЙЁ╣Й╡╘ К⌠╠Л²└ К╙╘Л═│Л°╪К║° М∙°К▀╓.
    <ul>
      <li>Л≤┬) Л≥╦Й╣░ Й╢─К═╗ Л┌╛Л²╢М┼╦Л≈░ Л∙┘Л└╠Л╫■К⌠°К╔╪ Л▀╛ЙЁ═ Л≥╦Й╣░К╤─ Й╢─ЙЁ└Л·░Й╟─ Л═▒Л├█М∙≤К╘╢ М∙╢К▀╧ PCЛ≈░ Л∙┘Л└╠Л╫■К⌠°К╔╪ Л└╓Л╧≤, Й╥╦ PCЛ≈░Л└° Л═∙КЁ╢К╔╪ К╧╪К┐└</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h1 id="dns-КЁ╢Л∙┬">DNS КЁ╢Л∙┬</h1>
<h2 id="1-dnsdomain-name-service-query">1. DNS(Domain Name Service) Query</h2>
<h3 id="1-dns-domain-name-service">1. DNS (Domain Name Service)</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Л²╦М└╟К└╥ К└╓М┼╦Л⌡▄М│╛Л┐│Л≈░Л└° Л╩╢М⌠╗М└╟Л²≤ Л²╢К╕└Л²└ IP Лё╪Л├▄К║° КЁ─М≥≤М∙≤Й╠╟К┌≤ М∙╢Л└²М∙≤К┼■ К█╟ Л┌╛Л ╘К░≤К┼■ К╤└Л┌╟ К└╓Л²╢К╟█ Л▀°Л┼╓М┘°</li>
  <li>URL Лё╪Л├▄Л≈░ К▄─М∙° IP Лё╪Л├▄К╔╪ Л∙▄К═╓Лё╪К┼■ Л└°К╧└Л┼╓</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">nslookup</code> : DNS М≥∙Л²╦ К▐└Й╣╛
    <ul>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">nslookup www.naver.com</code></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>DNS Л╖┬Л²≤ Л ╟Л└═Л┬°Л°└
    <ul>
      <li>Windows
        <ul>
          <li>DNS cache table М≥∙Л²╦ (<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ipconfig /displaydns</code>)</li>
          <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">C:\windows\system32\drivers\etc\hosts.ics</code> М▄▄Л²╪ К┌╢Л ╘ М≥∙Л²╦</li>
          <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">C:\windows\system32\drivers\etc\hosts</code> М▄▄Л²╪ К┌╢Л ╘ М≥∙Л²╦</li>
          <li>DNS Л└°К╡└Л≈░Й╡▄ Л╖┬Л²≤</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Linux
        <ul>
          <li>nscd(Name Service Cache Daemon) М≥∙Л²╦ (КЁ└К▐└ К█╟К╙╛ Л└╓Л╧≤М∙└Л ■)</li>
          <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/etc/hosts.conf</code> М▄▄Л²╪ К┌╢Л ╘ М≥∙Л²╦</li>
          <li>DNS Л└°К╡└Л≈░Й╡▄ Л╖┬Л²≤</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="2-dns-Й╣╛Л║╟">2. DNS Й╣╛Л║╟</h3>

<p><img src="/assets/images/posts/DNS_schema.svg.png" alt="DNS Schema" /></p>

<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domain_name">Л²╢К╞╦Л╖─ Л╤°Л╡≤</a></p>

<ul>
  <li>Root Domain(.) : К╙╗К⌠═ К▐└К╘■Л²╦Л²≤ Й╥╪КЁ╦Л²╢ К░≤К┼■ Л╣°Л┐│ Root level Domain</li>
  <li>Top Level Domain : com, org, kr К⌠╠Л²≤ Й╣╜Й╟─, Л╖─Л≈╜Л²└ К┌≤М┐─К┐└</li>
  <li>Second Level : Л┌╛Л ╘Л·░Й╟─ К▐└К╘■Л²╦ К╙┘Л²└ Л▀═Л╡╜М∙╢Л└° К⌠╠К║²М∙═ Л┬≤ Л·┬К┼■ Л≤│Л≈╜</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="3-dns-Л└°К╧└Л┼╓-К╟╘Л▀²">3. DNS Л└°К╧└Л┼╓ К╟╘Л▀²</h3>

<p><img src="/assets/images/posts/dns_query.gif" alt="DNS Query" /></p>

<p><a href="https://www.internetsociety.org/resources/deploy360/dns-privacy/intro/">Л²╢К╞╦Л╖─ Л╤°Л╡≤</a></p>

<ul>
  <li>DNS Query Л╒┘К╔≤
    <ul>
      <li>Recursive Query(Л┬°М≥≤) : Local DNS Л└°К╡└Л≈░ QueryК╔╪ КЁ╢К┌╢ Л≥└Л└╠К░° К▀╣Л²└ Л ■Л╡╜</li>
      <li>Iterative Query(К╟≤КЁ╣) : Local DNS Л└°К╡└Й╟─ К▀╓К╔╦ DNS Л└°К╡└Л≈░Й╡▄ QueryК╔╪ КЁ╢К┌╢Л√╢ К▀╣Л²└ Л ■Л╡╜, Л≥╦К╤─ К▐└К╘■Л²╦Л≈░Л└° Й╟°КЁ└Л═│Л²╦ Л·▒Л≈┘Л²└ М├╣М∙╢ Л═∙КЁ╢К╔╪ Л√╩Л√╢Л≥─ Л╒┘М∙╘М∙╢Л└° Л∙▄К═╓Л╓▄</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>DNS Query Л└╦К╤─ К╟╘Л▀²
    <ul>
      <li>М│╢К²╪Л²╢Л√╦М┼╦Й╟─ UDPК║° DNS RequestК╔╪ DNS ServerЛ≈░ Л═└Л├║</li>
      <li>DNS Л└°К╡└К┼■ DNS RequestЛ≈░ К▄─М∙╢Л└° DNS ResponseК║° Л²▒К▀╣, Л ■Л╡╜М∙° IP Лё╪Л├▄К╔╪ К└ёЛ√╢Л└° КЁ╢К┌╢Л╓▄</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>DNS Л╕²М▐╜ЙЁ╣Й╡╘
    <ul>
      <li>Л╤°К╟°Л╖─ IPК╔╪ VictimЛ²≤ IP (DNS Server) К║° КЁ─Л║╟М∙╗</li>
      <li>Open DNS Resolver Л└°К╡└К╔╪ Л²╢Л ╘</li>
      <li>DNS QueryЛ²≤ TypeЛ²└ Б─°ANYБ─²К║° Л└╓Л═∙
        <ul>
          <li>К▀╓Л√▒М∙° TYPEЛ²╦ A, NS, CNAME, AAAA К⌠╠Л²≤ К╙╗К⌠═ К═┬Л╫■К⌠°К╔╪ Л ■Л╡╜М∙≤Й╦╟ К∙▄К╛╦Л≈░ Л ■Л╡╜М∙° Л©╪К╕╛ М▄╗М┌╥КЁ╢К▀╓ М│╛Й╡▄ Л╕²М▐╜К░╗</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>DoS ЙЁ╣Й╡╘Л°╪К║°, DNS Reflector Attack Л²╢К²╪ЙЁ═К▐└ М∙╗</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>DNS К═┬Л╫■К⌠°</li>
</ul>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: left">Л╒┘К╔≤</th>
      <th style="text-align: left">К┌╢Л ╘</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">A(Address)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">М≤╦Л┼╓М┼╦ Л²╢К╕└Л²└ IPv4 Лё╪Л├▄К║° К╖╓М∙▒</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">AAAA(IPv6 Address)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">М≤╦Л┼╓М┼╦ Л²╢К╕└Л²└ IPv6 Лё╪Л├▄К║° К╖╓М∙▒</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">PTR(Reverse-lookup Pointer records)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">IP Лё╪Л├▄К╔╪ Й╦╟К╟≤Л°╪К║° К▐└К╘■Л²╦ Л²╢К╕└Л²└ Л╟╬К┼■ К█╟ Л┌╛Л ╘</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">NS(Name Server)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Лё╪Л√╢Л╖└ М≤╦Л┼╓М┼╦Л≈░ К▄─М∙° ЙЁ╣Л▀²Л═│Л²╦ Name ServerК╔╪ Л∙▄К═╓Л╓▄</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">MX(Mail Exchanger)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">DNS К▐└К╘■Л²╦ Л²╢К╕└Л≈░ К▄─М∙° К╘■Л²╪ Й╣░М≥≤ Л└°К╡└К╔╪ Л∙▄К═╓Л╓▄. Л²╢ Л═∙КЁ╢К┼■ SMTP Й╟─ Л═└Л·░ К╘■Л²╪Л²└ Л═│Л═┬М∙° М≤╦Л┼╓М┼╦К║° К²╪Л ╟М▄┘М∙≤К┼■К█╟ Л┌╛Л ╘.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">CNAME(Canonical Name)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">М≤╦Л┼╓М┼╦Л²≤ К▀╓К╔╦ Л²╢К╕└(КЁ└Л╧╜)Л²└ Л═∙Л²≤М∙≤К┼■ К█╟ Л┌╛Л ╘, AК═┬Л╫■К⌠°Л²≤ КЁ└К╙┘Л²└ К▀╛Л∙└ Лё╪К┼■ Й╡┐</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">SOA(Start of Authority)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">К▐└К╘■Л²╦Л≈░ К▄─М∙° Й╤▄М∙°Л²└ Й╟√К┼■ Л└°К╡└К╔╪ М▒°Л▀°М∙╗. К▐└К╘■Л²╦Л≈░Л└° Й╟─Л·╔М│╟ Й╤▄М∙°Л²└ К╤─Л≈╛К╟⌡Л²─ М≤╦Л┼╓М┼╦К╔╪ Л└═Л√╦ (Й╦╟КЁ╦ Name Server, К▐└К╘■Л²╦ Й╢─К╕╛Л·░Л²≤ Л═└Л·░К╘■Л²╪, К▐└К╘■Л²╦ Л²╪К═╗К╡┬М≤╦ К⌠╠ DNS М∙╣Л▀╛Л═∙КЁ╢)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Any(ALL)</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">Л°└Л²≤ К╙╗К⌠═ К═┬Л╫■К⌠°К╔╪ М▒°Л▀°</td>
